description:
"Cracker Barrel" (a once widely successful and household brand)... is now the subject of enormous political pressure, and public scandal. After rebranding themselves, and making a push for modernization, the business has become the target of a political influence machine in ways that almost *demand* a closer look at what's happening. 

While the business shift itself is certainly on shaky ground, the inexplicable perfect storm, (for a business that has found itself on the opposite sides of a political chasm over the past twenty years) is nothing short of a disaster.
